Engolon e tung'ani


1   Ore apa olasurai naa aing'en oleng alang ing'uesi pooki naaitobira Olaitoriani Enkai. Neikilikuan ninye enkitok ajoki, “Eji ketejo doi Enkai, ‘Eminya pooki ng'anayio lo lchani otii ena kurma?’ ”


2  Nejoki enkitok olasurai, “Aikiindim iyiook aainosa ilng'anayio pooki loo lkeek le nkurma, 
3  kake etejo Enkai, ‘Eminya ilo ng'anayioi leilo shani otii empolos enkurma, nimishoroo hoo ninye arashu iyeye.’ ” 
4  Kake etiaka olasurai enkitok, “Miyeye ntae; 
5  amu eyiolo Enkai ajo ore tininosinoso ninye nebolo inkonyek inyi, nitiuu anaa Enkai, niyiolouu isupati o ntorrok.”


6  Ore peyie edol enkitok ilo shani ajo sidai te ndaa, naa olchani sii oitiship inkonyek, naa olchani sii onguarrayu oiteng'en oltung'ani neitayu olng'anayioi lenyena neinos; neisho sii olpayian lenye embata, neinos ninye. 
7  Ore inkonyek e pokira nebolo, neyiolou ina kata aajo meishopo. Nerip mbenek olng'aboli aitaa nkilani. 
8  Nening ninche oltoilo lo Laitoriani Enkai elo te nkurma eiropija enkolong. Ore olpayian o enkitok enye neisudori peyie medol Enkai tiatua ilkeek le nkurma. 
9  Kake eipoto Olaitoriani Enkai ilo tungani nejoki ninye: “Kaji itii iyie?” 
10  Neng'amaa ajoki, “Atoning'o oltoilo lino te nkurma, naureishoyu amu atoduaa ajo maishopo naipirri aisudori.” 
11  Nejoki Enkai, “Aing'ae likitiaaka minchopo? Inosa o lng'anayioi lo lchani laitanapa apa intae ajoki eminya?” 
12  Nejo ilo tung'ani, “Ore ina kitok apa nikinchoo metaa tenebo nanu, ninye naaishoo olng'anayioi lo lchani, mainosa.”


13   Ina pee ejoki Olaitoriani Enkai enkitok, “Kaa bae ena nitaasa?” Nejo enkitok, “Olasurai laateleja nanya.”

Etudung'o Enkai enkiguana


14  Nejoki Olaitoriani Enkai olasurai, “Ore amu itaasa ena, kitediaaki iyie aaitulus too nkishu pooki o ng'uesi pooki entim, keaku iserpepiari te nkop, naa enterit ninye endaa ino, too nkolong'i pooki e nkishui ino. 
15   Ekapik olomang'ati erishata ino o enkitok. Neijia sii etiu erishata e ishoi ino o eishoi enye. Ekepurd ninye elukunya ino, ore iyie niony entutunyo enye.”


16  Nejoki ninye enkitok, “Kaaponiki nanu emion te ishoi ino, te mion sapuk iiu inkera. Ore iyieunot inono pooki keaku ino lpayian lino, neaku sii ninye likintore iyie.”


17   Nejoki ninye Adam, “Ore amu itoning'o oltoilo le nkitok ino, ninosa, ilo ng'anayioi lo lchani laaitanapa ajoki ‘Minya,’ etediaki enkop tenkaraki iyie, ekeaku enenkinyinyiret ake inya te nkishui ino pooki. 
18  Kebulu ilkiku o ntulele te nkurma, neaku inya nena aitubulu oo nkurman. 
19  Te nkinyinyiret inya endaa, ometaba anaa nirrinyokino enterit, amu teine apa kintobiruaki. Ira enterit naa enterit irrinyokino.”


20  Neisho ilo tung'ani enkitok enye enkarna ajo Hawa amu ninye ng'otonye oo looishu pooki. 
21  Neitobiraki Olaitoriani Enkai Adam o enkitok enye nkilani oo ndapan, neishopoki ninche.

Etaarayie Enkai Adam o Hawa aitung'uaa enkurma e Eden


22   Nejo Olaitoriani Enkai, “Ng'ura, etotiwuo oltung'ani anaa obo lang etayiolo isidain o ntorrok; ore tena kata, neidim ninye aitorioki enkaina enye olchani le nkishui ainosa, neishu ninye intarasi.” 
23  Metaa eitayio Olaitoriani Enkai ninye te nkurma e Eden peyie epuo aatur enkop apa naitobirunyeki ninche. 
24  Nearaa ninye ilo tung'ani. Ore te nkalo oloo saen e Eden, etipika ninye olmalaika, o lalem oyupuyup oman pooki alo peyie errip enkoitoi olchani le nkishui.

